om\": 802, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The outspoken presenter doubled down on his disdain for the country with his only positive appraisal coming from the cuisine.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are so rude.\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Oh, they are really up themselves\\u2026 they are pompous.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1048, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They do a good burger though.\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1078, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do like the burgers and stuff over here,\\\" he said,  Stefanovic, who hosted the Games' opening ceremony, said he enjoyed the \\\"blue Smurf with his aggots hanging out\\\", adding \\\"I mean, it just does not get better\\\".\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1292, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Sydney-born media personality's wife of six years Jasmine, 40, and daughter Harper accompanied him to the Paris Games in luxury Airbnb sponsored accommodation.\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1348, \"end\": 1355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasmine\", \"score\": 0.9999999939195732, \"rank\": 6.076065495159327e-09, \"text\": \"Jasmine\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasmine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasmine\"}, {\"begin\": 1426, \"end\": 1432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Airbnb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Airbnb\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Airbnb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Airbnb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jasmine on Instagram uploaded a photo with their daughter smiling on a hotel balcony during their lavish funded stay.\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1576, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A beautiful welcome to Paris by\\u00a0@airbnb\\u00a0thank you for hosting us during the\\u00a0@olympics.\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1602, \"end\": 1607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.177245029750482e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have made such amazing family memories already.\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1716, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It truly feels like a home away from home,\\\" the mother-of-one wrote.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1785, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She later copped flack after she uploaded a photo of the couple arm in arm with the Paris Eiffel tower in the background ahead of a dinner sponsored by Channel 9.\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1949, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"La Girafe with you,\\\" the shoe designer captioned the picture.\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 2013, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thank you @channel9 for a beautiful dinner.\\\"\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2060, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Girafe Restaurant is described as an upscale eatery, situated near the Palais de Chaillot with views of the Eiffel Tower, and specialises in gourmet seafood dishes.\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2226, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2133, \"end\": 2151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palais_de_Chaillot\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.104765057661774e-26, \"text\": \"Palais de Chaillot\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palais_de_Chaillot\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palais_de_Chaillot\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Menu items such as caviar cost up to AUD$1,000 and a seafood platter for two starring lobster is priced at almost $500, according to the menu on its website.\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2385, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jasmine was called out for the post which attracted criticism and anger from social media users arguing the dinner was poor timing given the negative spotlight on the network in recent weeks.\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2387, \"end\": 2394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasmine\", \"score\": 0.9999999939195732, \"rank\": 6.076065495159327e-09, \"text\": \"Jasmine\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasmine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasmine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am sure all the people who have just been sacked from Channel 9 will be happy to see you eating at the most expensive restaurant in Paris paid for by Channel 9,\\\" one wrote.\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2715, \"end\": 2720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.177245029750482e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Like read the room.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2777, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Go have dinner and enjoy yourself.\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2812, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But at least have enough compassion to not post about it,\\\" said another.\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2885, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes as Nine last month announced hundreds of job cuts as part of the network's cost-cutting plan - which will eliminate five per cent of the company's total work force, mostly from its metro newspapers and the Nine TV network.\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 3118, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The company\\u00a0attributed the cuts to the termination of a commercial deal with Meta, the owner of Facebook and Instagram, as well as a sluggish advertising market.\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3197, \"end\": 3201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meta_Platforms\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.280732471658226e-12, \"text\": \"Meta\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meta_Platforms\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meta_Platforms\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The axed Meta deal -which compensated Australian news publishers for content used on social media- was a lifeline for struggling networks and newspapers due to the decline in free-to-air linear broadcast audiences and shrinking newspaper circulations.\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3292, \"end\": 3296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meta_Platforms\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.280732471658226e-12, \"text\": \"Meta\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meta_Platforms\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meta_Platforms\"}, {\"begin\": 3321, \"end\": 3331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.99965118573265, \"rank\": 0.0003268184518862067, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To join the conversation, pleaselog in.Do not have an account?Register  Join the conversation, you are commenting asLogout  Our Apps\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3668, \"entities\": []}]}"